title: Kubernetes: Roles
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors the number of cluster roles, roles and the
 total number of roles in a kubernetes cluster. Levels for the
 individual numbers of roles can be defined in WATO.

discovery:
 One summary service is created.
